data.name: ToolStripButton19.ToolTipText
data.value:
Move 2D Object Up
(Note: The top most 2D object in the resource tree is drawn with deepest depth i.e. behind all other objects and the bottom most one is drawn with least depth i.e. above all objects. So arranging 2D objects help to define depths of objects.)
